{"id":128,"parent_id":124,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":128,"title":"Romans 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Abraham’s faith was accounted to him for righteousness—Man is justified by faith, righteous works, and grace."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.1","order":"03.08.004.15262"},["b","1"],"What shall we say then that Abraham our father, as pertaining to the flesh, hath found?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.2","order":"03.08.004.15263"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"For"],"if Abraham were justified by works, he hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},["i","whereof"],"to glory"],"; but not before God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.3","order":"03.08.004.15264"},["b","3"],"For what saith the scripture? Abraham",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"believed"],"God, and it was counted unto him for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.4","order":"03.08.004.15265"},["b","4"],"Now to him that worketh is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"reward"],"not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"reckoned"],"of grace, but of debt."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.5","order":"03.08.004.15266"},["b","5"],"But to him that worketh not, but believeth on him that justifieth the ungodly, his faith is counted for righteousness."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.6","order":"03.08.004.15267"},["b","6"],"Even as David also describeth the blessedness of the man, unto whom God imputeth righteousness without works,"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.7","order":"03.08.004.15268"},["b","7"],["i","Saying,"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Blessed"],["i","are"],"they whose iniquities are forgiven, and whose sins are covered."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.8","order":"03.08.004.15269"},["b","8"],"Blessed",["i","is"],"the man to whom the Lord will not impute sin."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.9","order":"03.08.004.15270"},["b","9"],["i","Cometh"],"this blessedness then upon the circumcision",["i","only,"],"or upon the uncircumcision also? for we say that faith was reckoned to Abraham for righteousness."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.10","order":"03.08.004.15271"},["b","10"],"How was it then reckoned? when he was in circumcision, or in uncircumcision? Not in circumcision, but in uncircumcision."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.11","order":"03.08.004.15272"},["b","11"],"And he received the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sign"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"circumcision"],", a seal of the righteousness of the faith which",["i","he had yet"],"being uncircumcised: that he might be the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"father"],"of all them that believe, though they be not circumcised; that righteousness might be imputed unto them also:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.12","order":"03.08.004.15273"},["b","12"],"And the father of circumcision to them who are not of the circumcision only, but who also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"walk"],"in the steps of that faith of our father Abraham, which",["i","he had"],"being",["i","yet"],"uncircumcised."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.13","order":"03.08.004.15274"},["b","13"],"For the promise, that he should be the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"heir"],"of the world,",["i","was"],"not to Abraham, or to his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"seed"],", through the law, but through the righteousness of faith."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.14","order":"03.08.004.15275"},["b","14"],"For if they which are of the law",["i","be"],"heirs, faith is made void, and the promise made of none effect:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.15","order":"03.08.004.15276"},["b","15"],"Because the law worketh wrath: for where no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"law"],"is,",["i","there is"],"no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"transgression"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.16","order":"03.08.004.15277"},["b","16"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Therefore"],["i","it is"],"of faith, that",["i","it might be"],"by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"grace"],"; to the end the promise might be sure to all the seed; not to that only which is of the law, but to that also which is of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"faith"],"of Abraham; who is the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"father"],"of us all,"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.17","order":"03.08.004.15278"},["b","17"],"(As it is written, I have made thee a father of many nations,) before him whom he believed,",["i","even"],"God, who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"quickeneth"],"the dead, and calleth those things which be not as though they were."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.18","order":"03.08.004.15279"},["b","18"],"Who against hope believed in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"hope"],", that he might become the father of many",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"nations"],", according to that which was spoken, So shall thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"seed"],"be."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.19","order":"03.08.004.15280"},["b","19"],"And being not weak in faith, he considered not his own body now dead, when he was about an hundred years",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"old"],", neither yet the deadness of Sara’s womb:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.20","order":"03.08.004.15281"},["b","20"],"He",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"staggered"],"not at the promise of God through unbelief; but was strong in faith, giving glory to God;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.21","order":"03.08.004.15282"},["b","21"],"And being fully persuaded that, what he had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"promised"],", he was able also to perform."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.22","order":"03.08.004.15283"},["b","22"],"And therefore it was imputed to him for righteousness."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.23","order":"03.08.004.15284"},["b","23"],"Now it was not written for his sake alone, that it was imputed to him;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.24","order":"03.08.004.15285"},["b","24"],"But for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"us"],"also, to whom it shall be imputed, if we believe on him that raised up Jesus our Lord from the dead;"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.25","order":"03.08.004.15286"},["b","25"],"Who was delivered for our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"offences"],", and was raised again for our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"justification"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.2a","order":"03.08.004.15287"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/4.2-5"},["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 4:2–5 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.2b","order":"03.08.004.15289"},["b","2b"],["span.small","GR"],"ground, reason for boasting."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.3a","order":"03.08.004.15291"},["b","3a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-gen/15.9-12"},["span.small","JST"],"Gen. 15:9–12 (Appendix)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.3b","order":"03.08.004.15293"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.4a","order":"03.08.004.15295"},["b","4a"],["span.small","GR"],"wage, hire."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.4b","order":"03.08.004.15297"},["b","4b"],["span.small","GR"],"considered a favor but as his due."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.7a","order":"03.08.004.15299"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/32.1"},"Ps. 32:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.11a","order":"03.08.004.15301"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/signs"},"TG Signs"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.11b","order":"03.08.004.15303"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.11c","order":"03.08.004.15305"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.10"},"Abr. 2:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.12a","order":"03.08.004.15307"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.13a","order":"03.08.004.15309"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/birthright"},"TG Birthright"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.13b","order":"03.08.004.15311"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.15a","order":"03.08.004.15313"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.13"},"Rom. 5:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.25"},"2 Ne. 9:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.17.12-24"},"Alma 42:17 (12–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.15b","order":"03.08.004.15315"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"TG Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.16a","order":"03.08.004.15317"},["b","16a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 4:16 Therefore",["i","ye are justified"],"of faith",["i","and works, through"],"grace, to the end the promise might be sure to all the seed; not to",["i","them"],"only",["i","who are"],"of the law, but to",["i","them"],"also",["i","who are"],"of the faith of Abraham; who is the father of us all,"],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.16b","order":"03.08.004.15319"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.16c","order":"03.08.004.15321"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"16d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.16d","order":"03.08.004.15323"},["b","16d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-patriarchal"},"TG Family, Patriarchal"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.17a","order":"03.08.004.15325"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.18a","order":"03.08.004.15327"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"TG Hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.18b","order":"03.08.004.15329"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/nations"},"TG Nations"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.18c","order":"03.08.004.15331"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.19a","order":"03.08.004.15333"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/old-age"},"TG Old Age"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.20a","order":"03.08.004.15335"},["b","20a"],["span.small","GR"],"doubted, hesitated."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.21a","order":"03.08.004.15337"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.14"},"Gen. 18:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.37"},"Luke 1:37"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promise"},"TG Promise"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.24a","order":"03.08.004.15339"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.25.24-27"},"3 Ne. 20:25 (24–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.25a","order":"03.08.004.15341"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.5"},"Isa. 53:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.45"},"Mark 10:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.25b","order":"03.08.004.15343"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justification"},"TG Justification"],"."]]}
